Class CallerInfo

  • public class CallerInfo
extends java.lang.Object

      • CallerInfo

        public CallerInfo(java.lang.String className,
          java.lang.String methodName,
          java.lang.String fileName,
          int lineNum)
        Create a new CallerInfo with the specified pieces of information. Only className is required - the rest can be set to null or -1.
        Parameters:
        className - the name of the class, required.
        methodName - the name of the method, optional.
        fileName - the name of the file, optional.
        lineNum - the line number, optional. (Set to a negative number for unspecified.)
